Class CustomerCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.tordbjorn.model.CustomerCategory

  • @Entity
public class CustomerCategory
extends java.lang.Object
    CustomerCategory Represents a category which a customer (@see Customer) may belong to. It's primary use is for a sale representative to keep track of good customers and "bad" customers - relative to the customers budget/spending.
